# Change Log
All changes to the public API of this tool will be documented here.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](http://keepachangelog.com/) 
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org/).

## [2.1]

Adds an option to use local files instead of fetching the regions from the
1KG servers.

## [2.0]

Major refactor. Fixed chromosome Y issues when merging VCFs. Now running
requires paths to working copies of TABIX, BGZIP, JAVA, GATK3, BCFTOOLS,
and a human reference FASTA file for GATK3.

## [1.1.2]

Removing chromosome Y regions until bugfix.
--no-cleanup option for debugging.

## [1.1.1]

Changed the location of tempfiles (always to `/tmp` now).
Handle CTRL-C and CalledProcessErrors gracefully and always do a cleanup.

## [1.1.0]

Changed the default `--threads` argument to 6.

## [1.0.0]

Initial release.
